<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">338</NUMEX>. Contribution by the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">General Fund</ENAMEX> to the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SMI</ENAMEX> trust
fund.--The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">General Fund</ENAMEX> makes a contribution to the SMI
