<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">General Fund</ENAMEX> does not receive anything of value from <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SMI</ENAMEX>. Instead,
the payment constitutes a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">General Fund</ENAMEX> subsidy of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SMI</ENAMEX> trust
fund. Since the payment is not demanded or earned, it is an other
financing <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">source</ENAMEX> to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SMI</ENAMEX> rather than a revenue.
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">339</NUMEX>. Examples of other payments of a similar nature (and also
