<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">old</ENAMEX>; and the payment by the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">General Fund</ENAMEX> to the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Railroad Retirement</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">Board</ENAMEX> for the vested dual benefit payments received by certain
