<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">340</NUMEX>. Transfer by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CCC</ENAMEX> to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Federal Crop Insurance Corporation</ENAMEX>.--The
