<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">resources</ENAMEX>. Therefore, the amount of the transaction equal to the
book value of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">PP&E</ENAMEX> surrendered is not recognized as a gain,
a revenue, or an other financing <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">source</ENAMEX>.
