will be reported as stewardship land. Examples of stewardship land
include land used as forests and <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">parks</ENAMEX>, and land used for wildlife
and grazing.


22
"Acquired for or in connection with" is defined as including
land acquired with the intent to construct general <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">PP&E</ENAMEX> and
