<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">ceases</ENAMEX>, and the account is removed from an <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">entity</ENAMEX>'s receivables.
(<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Treasury Financial Manual Supplement</ENAMEX>)
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">WRITE-OFF -An</ENAMEX> action to remove an amount from an <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">entity</ENAMEX>'s assets
